 Cluster centroids

 Number of instances and cluster distribution
Step 10: Visualizing Cluster
 Use the Visualize Cluster Assignments option to view the graphical representation of clusters.
 Observe how the dataset instances are grouped into four clusters based on Manhattan distance.
